{"version": 2, "width": 80, "height": 24, "timestamp": 1774044624, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm"}}
[0.018054, "o", "\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== smalltalk-channel MCP demo ===\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nTwo agents (scout + forge) coordinate via IRC using real MCP JSON-RPC.\r\nEach step is an actual tools/call request to the MCP server.\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;33m[scout → #gate]\u001b[0m Announcing a research task...\r\n"]
[7.049643, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[7.551968, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[forge → #gate]\u001b[0m Picking up the task...\r\n"]
[14.559854, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[15.060219, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.060372, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → who]\u001b[0m Checking who's online in #general...\r\n"]
[22.068701, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m users in #general (3): bandit, scout, forge\r\n"]
[22.569228, "o", "\r\n"]
[22.56935, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → #general]\u001b[0m Posting results...\r\n"]
[29.585275, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #general\r\n"]
[30.086311, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[scout → fetch_history]\u001b[0m Reading what forge posted...\r\n"]
[37.09586, "o", "  \u001b[0;34m3 message(s) from #general:\r\n\r\n[2026-03-20T22:10:58.077Z] <HistServ> forge [account: forge] joined the channel\r\n[2026-03-20T22:10:58.077Z] <forge> Research complete. irctokens wins (parse-only, no state). pydle best for bots. irc3 for plugin architectures. Recommending irctokens.\r\n[2026-03-20T22:10:58.077Z] <HistServ> forge quit (Quit: Claude Code shutting down)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.595295, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[scout → dm forge]\u001b[0m Sending a direct message...\r\n"]
[44.602805, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m DM sent to forge\r\n"]
[45.103292, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[scout → list_channels]\u001b[0m Listing joined channels...\r\n"]
[52.111717, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m joined channels (2): #general, #gate\r\n"]
[52.61229, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[forge → join]\u001b[0m Joining a per-project channel...\r\n"]
[59.635904, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m joined #irc-research\r\n"]
[60.13629, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[forge → topic]\u001b[0m Broadcasting task status via channel topic...\r\n"]
[67.158301, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m topic set in #general\r\n"]
[67.659235, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m[bandit → status]\u001b[0m Checking connection health...\r\n"]
[74.673984, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m connected to 127.0.0.1:6667 as bandit (uptime: 3s, channels: #general, #gate)\r\n\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== Demo complete ===\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nIn production with Claude Code:\r\n  HIGH priority (mentions, DMs, #gate) → Claude acts on them immediately\r\n  NORMAL (other channels) → throttled summaries, Claude reads when convenient\r\n  fetch_history → Claude catches up on missed messages\r\n  join/part → dynamic channel subscription per task\r\n  topic → shared state / status board for all agents in a channel\r\n\r\n"]
